16 posts	• Page 1 of 2 • 1, 2	What would you do?
by osamabinobama on Tue Mar 29, 2011 2:49 pm	([msg=55709]see What would you do?[/msg])
There is a runaway train headed for a junction. The default path of the train has five people on it and the alternative has one. You have the power to change the path of the train and kill one person instead of five. Will you?Note: If so, you are considered responsible for the death, but if not, are you responsible for the death of the five people?
