by Goatboy on Tue Mar 29, 2011 2:52 pm	([msg=55711]see Re: What would you do?[/msg])
Well either way people are going to die. And either way, I am responsible. I would rather have one die than 5. But since you are asking a question that looks so simple on the outside, I am assuming there is a follow-up question.
