by Gatito on Tue Mar 29, 2011 4:38 pm	([msg=55718]see Re: What would you do?[/msg])
@Goatboy : You murderer...Here is another version:A runway train is hurtling down a track towards five people. You are on a bridge under which it will pass, and you can stop it by dropping a heavy weight in front of it. As it happens, there is a very fat man next to you and your only way to stop the trolley is to push him over the bridge and onto the track, killing him to save five.
